data.description: Welcome to your new oasis! This beautifully maintained home has 3-bedrooms and a den, 2-bathrooms with 2,307 square feet and is the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality. Sunlight pours into this home, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The large windows and open floor plan ensure that every room is bathed in the beautiful Arizona sunlight, making the home feel bright and cheerful year-round. With three generous bedrooms and a den, this home offers ample space for both family living and entertaining. The versatile den can be used as a home office, a playroom, or even a guest room. The heart of this home is the stunning kitchen, complete with leathered granite countertops. With modern appliances, ample counter space, and plenty of storage, you'll enjoy cooking and... entertaining in this kitchen! Step outside to your backyard oasis and enjoy the tranquility of desert living. The covered patio is perfect for al fresco dining and relaxation. The newer articifial turf provides a safe place for the kids to play, entertain friends or just relax and is very private with being built up above the street and rear neighbors. Very easy commute to I-10, Davis Monthan AFB, schools, shopping and more!
